OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FA driver has been jailed after
OL,7,Fploughing into a pedestrian at high
OL,8,Fspeed - leaving him with injuries so
OL,9,Fsevere he needed his leg amputated.
OL,11,FRaymond Buckley, 63, was walking home
OL,12,Ffrom a New Year's Eve celebration in
OL,13,FWinsford, Cheshire, when he was hit by
OL,14,Fthe car driven by Anthony Abbott on
OL,15,Fthe A54 High Street, near Collingham
OL,16,FWay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FAlongside losing his leg due to the
OL,7,Fimpact, Mr Buckley suffered multiple
OL,8,Fbroken ribs, fractures to the bones in
OL,9,Fhis right hand and left thigh, and a
OL,10,Fdisplaced fracture of his upper jaw.
OL,12,FInstead of stopping Abbott, 45, set
OL,13,Fabout trying to cover his tracks
OL,14,Ffollowing the incident - attempting to
OL,15,Fget rid of his car - all of which was
OL,16,Fcaught on CCTV.
OL,18,FBut, following an investigation Abbott
OL,19,Fwas caught, and he admitted causing
OL,20,Fserious injury by careless driving at
OL,21,FChester Crown Court on 23 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FBut he was not prosecuted for a more
OL,7,Fserious charge of dangerous driving
OL,8,Fdue to "insufficient evidence".
OL,10,FHe also pleaded guilty to committing a
OL,11,Fseries of acts with intent to pervert
OL,12,Fthe course of justice.
OL,14,FChester Crown Court heard how officers
OL,15,Flaunched an investigation to find the
OL,16,Fcar and its driver after a car wing
OL,17,Fmirror was found among the debris,
OL,18,Fbelieved to belong to a Volkswagen, at
OL,19,Fthe scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FCCTV revealed a darkcoloured
OL,7,FVolkswagen Eos travelling at speed
OL,8,Ftowards the incident shortly before it
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FFootage then shows it speeding away
OL,12,Fthrough the town, arriving in the
OL,13,FPlantagenet Close area at around
OL,14,F11.58pm.
OL,16,FAt 12.01am, a black Vauxhall Corsa
OL,17,Fleft the same address, and was caught
OL,18,Fon CCTV pulling up to the scene of the
OL,19,Fincident where emergency services were
OL,20,Fnow responding, before returning to
OL,21,FPlantagenet Close.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FThe Volkswagen was later captured on
OL,7,FCCTV footage at around 1.47am pulling
OL,8,Finto an industrial park in the
OL,9,FEardswick Lane area of Crewe.
OL,11,FAbbott, who had now been identified as
OL,12,Fthe vehicle's owner, was seen leaving
OL,13,Fthe car before removing an e-bike from
OL,14,Fthe passenger side and riding away.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FAt around 9.30am the same day, Abbott
OL,7,Freturned to the industrial site with
OL,8,Fanother man in a flatbed truck where
OL,9,Ffootage showed him driving the
OL,10,FVolkswagen onto the back of the truck,
OL,11,Fsecuring it and then using tape to
OL,12,Fcover its number plate.
OL,14,FThe same truck - which was no longer
OL,15,Fcarrying any cargo - was stopped by
OL,16,Fofficers in the Fenton area of
OL,17,FStokeonTrent on 2 January, with
OL,18,FAbbott found inside alongside a
OL,19,F42yearold man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FBoth men were arrested and taken back
OL,7,Fto Cheshire for interview, and
OL,8,Fofficers seized the e-bike and items
OL,9,Fof clothing worn by Abbott on the
OL,10,Fnight of the offence.
OL,12,FMessages found on Abbott's phone
OL,13,Frevealed he had discussed plans to
OL,14,Fpurchase an identical Volkswagen Eos
OL,15,Fto the one involved in the collision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FThe Volkswagen involved in the
OL,7,Fcollision was later discovered in
OL,8,FFenton, close to where Abbott had been
OL,9,Farrested, with the nearside wing
OL,10,Fmirror missing and damage to the front
OL,11,Fbumper.
OL,13,FThe 42yearold man, from
OL,14,FStokeonTrent, was found not guilty
OL,15,Fof committing a series of acts with
OL,16,Fintent to pervert the course of
OL,17,Fjustice and assisting an offender.
OL,19,FAbbott declined to answer any
OL,20,Fquestions during interview.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to three years in
OL,7,Fprison and has been banned from
OL,8,Fdriving for four years and six months.
OL,10,FDetective Constable Hannah Lamborn, of
OL,11,Fthe Roads and Crime Unit, said: "In
OL,12,Fwhat was meant to be a night of
OL,13,Fcelebration, New Year's Eve 2025 was
OL,14,Fone full of tragedy that resulted in
OL,15,Fthe victim in this case, a sociable
OL,16,Fand outgoing familiar face known
OL,17,Facross Winsford, having had his life
OL,18,Fcompletely changed forever.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,F"The effects of Anthony Abbot's
OL,7,Fblatant disregard for basic road
OL,8,Fsafety are long-lasting and go well
OL,9,Fbeyond the physical.
OL,11,F"Abbott's careless actions have not
OL,12,Fonly resulted in another man losing
OL,13,Fhis leg but also his sense of
OL,14,Findependence and the freedom to pursue
OL,15,Fthe many of the activities he enjoyed.
OL,16,FThere is no sentence or conviction
OL,17,Fthat can make up for that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,F"With that in mind, the victim has
OL,7,Fshown a tremendous amount of
OL,8,Fresilience throughout our entire
OL,9,Finvestigation, assisting officers with
OL,10,Ftheir enquiries and having to relive
OL,11,Fthe events of New Year's Eve. Both he,
OL,12,Fand his family, remain in our thoughts
OL,13,Fas they begin their long journey of
OL,14,Fhealing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777075397
OL,3,CDriver jailed after collision which
OL,4,Cleft man needing amputation
OL,6,F"I would also like to take this
OL,7,Fopportunity to thank our colleagues
OL,8,Ffrom the North West Ambulance Service
OL,9,Fand Response officers who dealt with
OL,10,Fthe immediate aftermath of this
OL,11,Fdistressing incident with the utmost
OL,12,Fprofessionalism.
OL,14,F"Finally, my thanks go to the team of
OL,15,Fofficers assigned to this case whose
OL,16,Ftireless efforts enabled us to put all
OL,17,Fthe pieces of this puzzle together and
OL,18,Ffind and arrest the suspect within 48
OL,19,Fhours of the horrific offence
OL,20,Foccurring."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
